column7: Hey Teekay,  Unfortunately the nights you have asked for are taken now.  I would be happy to give you another date if you want to re-apply.  Full disclosure, you might just be a little cool for Gravity.  My wife and I love R&B and hip hop but the crowd we get is generally more jazz, singer-songwriter and folk.  In no way am I trying to put you off applying and I will book you, you just might be at the mercy of your own friends and fans for a draw though.  Be well.  Andy
